**TASK TRIAGE:**
During Intake & Planning (Workflow step 1), assess task complexity to determine process depth:

| Complexity | Examples | Process |
|---|---|---|
| **Trivial** | Aliases, single-line config tweaks, dotfile edits | Implement → Sign-Off (skip BDS loop) |
| **Standard** | New scripts, multi-file changes, tooling | Full BDS workflow (steps 2–5) |
| **Complex** | New features, security-sensitive code, architectural changes | Full BDS + iterate until all tests pass |

The BDS loop adds safety; skip it when there's no meaningful security or correctness surface to test. Trust your judgment.

